measures.expression:

{

measures.name: Keystone T12M MS% (Towable)
measures.expression:
VAR EndDate =
MAX ( 'Date'[Calendar Date])       -- <-- uses the row’s month in the visual

VAR T12MWindow =
DATESINPERIOD (
'Date'[Calendar Date],
EndDate,
-12,
MONTH
)

VAR TotalT12M =
CALCULATE (
[Towable Registration],
T12MWindow
)

VAR THORT12M =
CALCULATE (
[Keystone Towable Registration],
T12MWindow
)

RETURN
DIVIDE ( THORT12M, TotalT12M )
